Posts.Content: May 1, 2019 02:06PM Leidy wrote: I do not want to scare you, so please don't freak out, but my issues started with a "pinging" feeling, like shooting sharp pains, in my right breast, and that's where the tumor was. I waited way too long to look into it. I would definitely ask for a mammogram and/or an ultrasound if you have dense breasts, Just to be sure for your peace of mind.
